# UX (B2C daily-use)

- **Mobile-first**: primary flows must work one-handed on narrow viewports; defer desktop-only enhancements.
- **Onboarding**: shortest path to first success; show progress; allow skip where safe.
- **Trust**: clear pricing, privacy, and data use; explicit consent for sensitive actions.
- **Empty & error states**: every list/dashboard needs helpful empty copy + one primary action; errors are actionable (retry, contact, fix input).
- **Performance perception**: skeletons or optimistic UI for slow network; avoid blocking full page on minor updates.
- **Notifications**: prefer in-app toasts/banners; push only when value is high (PWA).
